<h1>Aardvark Firefox Extension</h1>
	<p id="whatitis">The Aardvark Firefox extension is a tool for web developers/designers as well as casual users.
To quickly see it in action on this page, <a href="javascript:document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(document.createElement('script')).setAttribute('src','http://www.karmatics.com/aardvark/bookmarklet.js')" title="in-page demo of aardvark">run the demo</a>.</p>

	<div id="installbox">
	<p id="install"><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/4111" target="_new" id="button"><span>Install Now</span></a><p>
	</div>
</div><!-- end intro -->


